[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1357},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":1333,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220517\u002F432259079\u002F":1342},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F05\u002F17\u002Fcomplete-express-imgur-upload-tutorial\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1317,"date":1318,"description":18,"extension":1319,"lang":1320,"meta":1321,"navigation":799,"path":1322,"readingMinutes":1323,"seo":1324,"standalone":1325,"stem":1326,"tags":1327,"tldr":1330,"updated":1330,"url":1331,"__hash__":1332},"content\u002FNodejs\u002F超完整-Express-Imgur-套件上傳教學.md","超完整 Express Imgur 套件上傳教學","432259079",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1301},"minimark",[11,15,19,27,31,36,39,42,45,52,55,61,64,70,73,78,81,87,91,94,100,103,109,112,117,120,126,130,142,150,153,159,162,190,197,203,214,220,232,238,242,250,257,274,277,283,286,292,295,304,307,313,317,320,337,340,344,353,356,359,362,538,545,548,554,557,568,752,756,759,768,771,987,990,993,997,1000,1009,1012,1019,1028,1031,1238,1241,1244,1250,1253,1260,1267,1270,1297],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"Imgur 是一個非常好用的網路相簿服務，主要有提供免費的圖片儲存服務，開發上也可以拿來當作上傳練習，甚至是 Blog 文章的圖片儲存庫，所以這一篇就來分享一下在 Express 的 Imgur 的圖片上傳教學。",[20,21,24],"callout",{"title":22,"type":23},"Note","note",[16,25,26],{},"本系列是針對 Imgur 來做介紹，但是 Imgur 在 2025 年 05 月 16 日之後限制台灣 IP 使用者無法上傳圖片，因此如果你是台灣使用者的話，可能會無法使用 Imgur 上傳圖片，這邊建議可以改用其他圖片上傳服務。",[12,28,30],{"id":29},"imgur-事前準備","Imgur 事前準備",[32,33,35],"h3",{"id":34},"imgur-album-建立","Imgur Album 建立",[16,37,38],{},"一開始先來學一下如何建立 Album，因此等一下後面上傳圖片都會指定到特定的 Album 中統一管理。",[16,40,41],{},"其實 Imgur 早期是可以直接建立一個 Album，但是後來不知道為什麼隱藏了 Album，按鈕並且非常難建立 Album，所以這一個流程基本上有八成以上的人找不到，所以會建議你務必依據以下流程來操作。",[16,43,44],{},"首先請你先登入 Imgur 網站，登入成功後點一下使用者列表中的「images」選項",[16,46,47],{},[48,49],"img",{"alt":50,"src":51},"images","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172151.png",[16,53,54],{},"接下來找到「All images」的下拉選單，裡面會有一個「New Album」點它",[16,56,57],{},[48,58],{"alt":59,"src":60},"New Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172202.png",[16,62,63],{},"會跳出一個關於 Album 相關的設定視窗，你就依照欄位填寫完畢之後按下 Save",[16,65,66],{},[48,67],{"alt":68,"src":69},"Album","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F202205172203.png",[16,71,72],{},"新增成功之後你就會看到一片空白，因為當前顯示的 Album 是你剛剛新增的 Album，而我們並沒有新增任何圖片進去，自然就會是空的無誤",[16,74,75],{},[48,76],{"alt":68,"src":77},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.04.30.png",[16,79,80],{},"恭喜你這樣子就成功建立了一個 Album。",[16,82,83],{},[84,85,86],"del",{},"Imgur 的使用者體驗真棒",[32,88,90],{"id":89},"imgur-album-id-取得","Imgur Album ID 取得",[16,92,93],{},"由於我們稍後會需要將圖片上傳到特定 Album，所以會需要 Album 的 ID，因此請先點一下使用者列表的「gallery profile」",[16,95,96],{},[48,97],{"alt":98,"src":99},"gallery profile","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_08.png",[16,101,102],{},"接下來在右側找到「Albums」",[16,104,105],{},[48,106],{"alt":107,"src":108},"Albums","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_10.png",[16,110,111],{},"接下來就是點一下「Posts」=> 「All」，不意外第一個就是你剛剛建立的 Album",[16,113,114],{},[48,115],{"alt":68,"src":116},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_11.png",[16,118,119],{},"進入到 Album 之後你可以看一下它的網址，我們只需要下方圖片紅框圈起來部分就好，那部分就是我們要找的 Album ID，這邊就請先記憶著，稍後 Express 時會使用到",[16,121,122],{},[48,123],{"alt":124,"src":125},"Album ID","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_13.png",[32,127,129],{"id":128},"註冊-imgur-應用程式","註冊 Imgur 應用程式",[16,131,132,133,137,138,141],{},"接下來我們要來註冊一個 Imgur 應用程式，因為我們會需要 ",[134,135,136],"code",{},"client_id"," 和 ",[134,139,140],{},"client_secret"," 來上傳圖片，你可以點一下下方連結進入註冊",[16,143,144],{},[145,146,129],"a",{"href":147,"rel":148},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Faddclient",[149],"nofollow",[16,151,152],{},"進入之後你會看到這個畫面",[16,154,155],{},[48,156],{"alt":157,"src":158},"註冊","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-05-17%2022.18.24.png",[16,160,161],{},"需要填寫的欄位如下",[163,164,165,174,182],"ul",{},[166,167,168,169],"li",{},"Application name\n",[163,170,171],{},[166,172,173],{},"任意名字",[166,175,176,177],{},"Authorization type\n",[163,178,179],{},[166,180,181],{},"選 OAuth 2 authorization without a callback URL",[166,183,184,185],{},"Email\n",[163,186,187],{},[166,188,189],{},"聯絡你用",[16,191,192,193,196],{},"ps.如果你「Authorization type」是選「Anonymous usage without user authorization」的話，那「Authorization callback URL」就要填入「",[134,194,195],{},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com","」",[16,198,199],{},[48,200],{"alt":201,"src":202},"申請應用程式","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_22.png",[16,204,205,206,137,208,210,211,213],{},"申請之後你會看到這個畫面，請記好你的 ",[134,207,136],{},[134,209,140],{},"，尤其是 ",[134,212,140],{}," 不可以搞丟，如果搞丟就只能重新生成而已",[16,215,216],{},[48,217],{"alt":218,"src":219},"申請成功","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_23.png",[16,221,222,223,225,226,231],{},"那麼這樣就申請完畢了，如果真的不小心遺失 ",[134,224,140],{}," 的話，可以點這個 ",[145,227,230],{"href":228,"rel":229},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002Faccount\u002Fsettings\u002Fapps",[149],"連結"," 到「Applications」中點一下「generate new secret」重新生成",[16,233,234],{},[48,235],{"alt":236,"src":237},"重新生成 client_secret","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_26.png",[32,239,241],{"id":240},"imgur-refresh-token-取得","Imgur Refresh Token 取得",[16,243,244,245,137,247,249],{},"前面我們已經準備了 ",[134,246,136],{},[134,248,140],{},"，但實際上還需要最後一樣鑰匙也就是 Refresh Token，而會需要 Refresh Token 是因為 Imgur 提供的 Token 是有時間限制的，那為了讓它可以自動刷新 Token，所以就必需要 Refresh Token 才可以。",[16,251,252,253,256],{},"取得 Refresh Token 的方式很特別，你需要將以下連結中的 「",[134,254,255],{},"${Client ID}","」換成我們剛剛申請的 Client ID",[258,259,264],"pre",{"className":260,"code":261,"language":262,"meta":263,"style":263},"language-html shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Fauthorize?client_id=${Client ID}&response_type=token\n","html","",[134,265,266],{"__ignoreMap":263},[267,268,271],"span",{"class":269,"line":270},"line",1,[267,272,261],{"class":273},"s8XSl",[16,275,276],{},"然後貼到瀏覽器網址列上按下 Enter 送出",[16,278,279],{},[48,280],{"alt":281,"src":282},"網址列","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_30.png",[16,284,285],{},"這時候你會進入到一個警告畫面，只要確定這是你要用的應用程式就好，若沒問題就按下允許",[16,287,288],{},[48,289],{"alt":290,"src":291},"允許","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_31.png",[16,293,294],{},"允許之後你會被跳回 Imgur 的畫面，然後你把當前畫面的 Url 複製下來，基本上會這麼長",[258,296,298],{"className":260,"code":297,"language":262,"meta":263,"style":263},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002F#access_token=xxxxx&expires_in=xxxxx&token_type=bearer&refresh_token=xxxxx&account_username=xxxx&account_id=xxxx\n",[134,299,300],{"__ignoreMap":263},[267,301,302],{"class":269,"line":270},[267,303,297],{"class":273},[16,305,306],{},"但這邊注意看，我們只需要 Refresh Token 就好，把它記錄下來，稍後也會使用到",[16,308,309],{},[48,310],{"alt":311,"src":312},"Refresh Token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FNodejs\u002F%E8%B2%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%83%8F_2022_5_17_22_32.png",[12,314,316],{"id":315},"imgur-最後確認","Imgur 最後確認",[16,318,319],{},"最後這邊確定下流程，如果你有依照文章流程下來的話，你應該完成了以下動作",[163,321,322,325,328,331,334],{},[166,323,324],{},"建立一個空的 Album",[166,326,327],{},"取得 Album ID",[166,329,330],{},"取得 Client ID",[166,332,333],{},"取得 Client Secret",[166,335,336],{},"取得 Refresh Token",[16,338,339],{},"上述這幾樣基本上缺一不可，如果有缺少的話，可以再往前看一下 Imgur 流程。",[12,341,343],{"id":342},"express-imgur","Express Imgur",[16,345,346,347,352],{},"本身 Imgur 官方是有提供 API 可以給我們使用的，但是其實實際開發上如果有現成套件的話，基本上就會選擇用套件較快，而這邊我們會使用的就是「",[145,348,351],{"href":349,"rel":350},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.npmjs.com\u002Fpackage\u002Fimgur",[149],"Imgur","」這個同名套件，這邊我會區分成兩個版本提供範例程式碼。",[16,354,355],{},"Imgur 套件基本上有兩個版本，分別是 1.x 跟 2.x 的寫法，但大多網路上都是 1.x。",[32,357,358],{"id":358},"前端範例程式碼",[16,360,361],{},"而這邊前端範例程式都是如下參考，HTML 部分就不額外提供了。",[258,363,367],{"className":364,"code":365,"language":366,"meta":263,"style":263},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","const formData = new FormData();\n  formData.append('file-to-upload', e.target.form[0].files[0]);\n  axios.post('\u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Fupload', formData, {\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'multipart\u002Fform-data',\n    },\n  })\n  .then((data) => {\n    console.log(data)\n  })\n  .catch(error => console.log(error));\n","js",[134,368,369,392,422,439,445,460,466,472,497,509,514],{"__ignoreMap":263},[267,370,371,375,379,382,385,389],{"class":269,"line":270},[267,372,374],{"class":373},"sOudu","const",[267,376,378],{"class":377},"stw71"," formData",[267,380,381],{"class":373}," =",[267,383,384],{"class":373}," new",[267,386,388],{"class":387},"scAaK"," FormData",[267,390,391],{"class":273},"();\n",[267,393,395,398,401,404,408,411,414,417,419],{"class":269,"line":394},2,[267,396,397],{"class":273},"  formData.",[267,399,400],{"class":387},"append",[267,402,403],{"class":273},"(",[267,405,407],{"class":406},"sWayO","'file-to-upload'",[267,409,410],{"class":273},", e.ta